  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is

        -  to determine the rate of osteoporosis among patients with advanced prostate cancer.

        -  to propose an algorithm for early detection of patients with advanced prostate cancer
           who are at risk of developing osteoporosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with advanced prostate cancer are included at the initiating of androgen deprivation
      therapy.

      The patients are followed for 2 years after inclusion with blood sampling, DXA-scan,
      questionnaire, bone scintigraphy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
