  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Prostate cancer

          -  Initiation of androgen deprivation therapy

          -  Oral and written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  They withdraw their consent

          -  Treatment for osteoporosis within the last year

          -  Other malignancy

          -  Other bone disease, bedbound, use of steroid
